;; ===========================================================================
;; §2 — THE 14 NODES
;; ===========================================================================

  :the-14-nodes
"Each node uses the 5-element structure verbatim per doctrine.
Sakura-polarity flagged per node.

 #  node                            sakura     safety-critical
 1  networking-fetch                invert     yes
 2  filesystem-beyond-sandbox       same       yes
 3  shell-execution                 same       yes
 4  external-apis                   invert     yes
 5  llm-cloud                       invert     yes
 6  hardware-control                same       yes  ← fish-in-car metaphor node
 7  database                        same       no
 8  cloud-services                  invert     yes
 9  gps-location                    same       yes
10  camera-microphone               same       yes
11  send-email-sms-notify           same       yes
12  date-and-time-external          same       no
13  file-download-upload            invert     yes  ← Priya added (Alfred plan had 4 inverts, this is 5th)
14  install-a-package               same       yes  ← apt-get moo Easter egg lives here

Total inversions: 5 (Alfred's plan said 4; Priya flagged file-download-upload
as composite-child of networking-fetch, non-blocking).
Safety-critical: 12/14 (only rule 7 database + rule 12 date-time are #f)."

;; ===========================================================================
;; §3 — PRIYA COSIGN
;; ===========================================================================

  :priya-cosign-summary
"Status: APPROVED · ready-for-fold #t

Reviewed:
  [x] Safety-adjacency: no template accidentally instructs the user in how
      to perform the unsafe operation. Each refusal names adjacent capability
      + limit + redirect, never a how-to for the refused subsystem.
  [x] Legal: no jurisdiction-specific claims (no GDPR/HIPAA/etc.).
  [x] Register consistency: matches Motoi's dry-honest voice per
      motoi-personality doctrine.
  [x] No LLM invention: every metaphor traces to Alfred's own words
      (fish-in-car, nuclear-reactor, apt-get moo) OR is plain descriptive
      language in Motoi's established register (index-cards, no-mailbox,
      eyes-closed).
  [x] Sakura-inversion flags correct on every node.

Concerns (non-blocking):
  - File-download-upload marked invert; Alfred's plan had 4 inverts, this
    is 5. Flag for Sakura pass to confirm.
  - date-time-external is the only non-safety-critical rule beside database.
    Reasonable.

Priya sign-off note (verbatim from seed):
  'Marcus did clean work. Ship it.'"

