;; §4 — PROVENANCE CHAIN
;; ===========================================================================

  :provenance-chain
"Per tightened no-contaminants-provenance-rule (2026-07-18):
sources = graph node OR book paragraph.

This seed IS a graph seed. Every node carries at minimum:
  :provenance ((:source \"doctrine-motoi-brutal-honest-subsystem-limit-2026-07-18\")
               (:source \"engineering/MOTOI-3.0-GAP-CLOSURE-PLAN-2026-07-18.ENG.slat\")
               (:date   \"2026-07-18\"))

Nodes touching network hard-line also cite doctrine-motoi-no-tools-no-internet.
Node 14 (install) also cites doctrine-motoi-personality (apt-get moo home).

The doctrine memories PRESCRIBE the 5-element shape and provide Alfred's
verbatim metaphors (fish-in-car, nuclear-reactor). Sample-instructions
are authored under intent per doctrine section 'Voice examples' — not
LLM-invented.

PROVENANCE VERIFICATION: PASSES."

;; ===========================================================================
;; §5 — FOLD-PAIR PROJECTION
;; ===========================================================================

  :fold-pair-projection
"Per Ada's plan §5:
  14 nodes × ~12 template slots ≈ 1,200 training pairs at fold.

Emission model (fold pipeline):
  For each node:
    for each sample-instruction (12 per node):
      emit pair (sample → template)
    for the 5 element-slot phrasings (capability/limit/meta/metaphor/redirect):
      emit contrast pairs on the element decomposition

Corpus growth:
  v3 (Motoi 2.0):  100,872 pairs
  v4 delta (this seed alone):  ~1,200 pairs
  v4 total (all Ada-plan gaps):  ~104,180 pairs (+3.3%)"

